  "read_only_context_before": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01634:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n拍频讨论的是[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01635:d166dd4fdc8f]]，它等于两个频率之差：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01636:d170ff937877]]，而主频约为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01637:fca1c53afb2c]]。这表示每秒会听到 2 次明显的强弱变化；但真正声音本身的振动并不慢，它的主频仍接近 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01638:d57d216a39cd]]。\n所以[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01639:58fbb96100c6]]并不等于[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01640:88948dc9ffcc]]。拍频题里一定要先把[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01641:70a757acc6fd]]和[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01642:265ffbde1dec]]分开看。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01643:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}",
